Get settlements of Ivory Coast

Source: R/get_settlements.R
get_settlements.Rd

Get settlements of Ivory Coast

get_settlements(url = steer$url[steer$level == 4])

Arguments

url

URL of source map dataset for settlements for Ivory Coast. This is set to the URL specified in the internal steering file data included in the package which provides the URL from the Humanitarian Data Exchange.

Value

A SpatialPointsDataFrame class object for the settlements for Ivory Coast

Examples

# Get settlements for Ivory Coast
get_settlements()
